Degradation of experience from my user perspective since 2 yrs. I use Teams for work, so intensive. It started with delays (I would receive messages on my phone hours after they were delivered to PC) and recently it peaked with Teams detecting my device as rooted, wich obviously it is not. It is recommending as solution the factory reset (lol). So I no longer have Teams on mobile. Maybe one of my apps is triggering the Teams false positive, but I cannot let Teams rule my phone or my life.
